data.title: Kris Jenner Packs on the PDA With Corey Gamble During Summer Vacay
data.meta_description: Kris Jenner and boyfriend Corey Gamble enjoyed a romantic trip to Italy in August. See the momager's sweet pic of the two and look back at their relationship.
data.text:
Kris Jenner and Corey Gamble are living la dolce vita.

The Kardashian-Jenner matriarch recently shared photos from the couple's August vacation in Italy, including a pic of the two kissing on a boat. During their trip, they visited the town of Portofino, where they met up with old friends. In fact, Kris posted an image of herself and Dolce & Gabbana co-founder Domenico Dolce sitting together while enjoying the sights of the Italian Riviera.

Kris, whose family celebrated Kourtney Kardashian and Travis Barker's wedding at Domenico and partner Stefano Gabbana's estate in Portofino in Italy in 2022, captioned her Aug. 31 post, "Magical moments in August."
